POLOKWANE – It’s set to be another cool week in Polokwane. According to People’s Weather’s forecast, temperatures will remain in the high teens and low twenties for the rest of the week.  Saturday will drop to a maximum of 18ºC while Tuesday and Wednesday will be the warmest days of the week at 20ºC. Minimum temperatures will peak at single digits this week, varying between 6ºC and 7ºC. Monday will be partly cloudy, while clear skies and sunny conditions are expected for the rest of the week. 